&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Service Mindset&lt;/strong&gt; - You enjoy being in service and supporting the needs of others efficiently and effectively. You are a self-starter and are able to work independently.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;People Person – &lt;/strong&gt;You are energized by working with collaborative people, and you enjoy building relationships and rapport with different types of people. It is natural for you to build an understanding of what people need and how you can help them.&lt;/li&gt;
